  <brief_title>A Study to Determine the Effect of WelChol Tablets on Cholesterol in Patients Who Have Been Taking Simvastatin for at Least 4 Weeks.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of WelCholÂ® as an Add-on to Simvastatin Therapy</official_title>
