  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to determine the effect of WelChol tablets on serum lipids,
      lipoproteins, apolipoproteins, and lipoprotein particle size in patients who were stabilized
      on simvastatin therapy for at least 4 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
